I was going to
fight for this one.

750
01:11:21,377 --> 01:11:24,187
<i>But the baby</i>
<i>started coming too early.</i>

751
01:11:25,047 --> 01:11:27,459
<i>Your</i> dat <i>wanted</i>
<i>to fetch Ella Mae,</i>

752
01:11:27,516 --> 01:11:29,860
<i>but I knew</i>
<i>something was wrong.</i>

753
01:11:31,987 --> 01:11:35,025
<i>I just knew I</i>
<i>needed an English doctor.</i>

754
01:11:39,361 --> 01:11:41,898
