<i>him not to leave me.</i>

755
01:11:42,498 --> 01:11:44,034
<i>But he did.</i>

756
01:11:44,833 --> 01:11:46,073
<i>He did leave me.</i>

757
01:11:47,336 --> 01:11:50,283
