<i>baby girl was born,</i>

758
01:11:50,406 --> 01:11:53,353
<i>but something was</i>
<i>wrong with her heart.</i>

759
01:11:54,176 --> 01:11:56,520
<i>There was</i>
<i>nothing they could do.</i>

760
01:11:57,613 --> 01:11:59,820
<i>She lived</i>
<i>only a few minutes.</i>

761
